{"tid":893280,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句 Diablo真係過哂時","createTime":"2018-11-07T13:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T21:10:23.000Z","uid":44068,"like":9,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b35c12d0635215c979e01a316896caa731ef2a12","tid":893280,"uid":44068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:27:40.000Z","msg":"Diablo 故事已經唔正<br />\n當年岩岩出有拍賣場個陣<br />\n戰鬥風格都岩果個年代玩法<br />\n但係依家2018黎講<br />\n咁既戰鬥系統  畫面都真係過晒時<br />\n唔岩依家依代人玩<br />\n近年所有大作都係玩畫面 玩戰鬥系統<br />\n巫師3 刺客教條依d單機驚都好重視畫面品質同戰鬥風格<br />\n就算講online驚係得番黑沙多d人玩<br />\n但黑沙無劇情無副本<br />\n戰鬥系統唔差 畫面極靚 技能招式係真係一個招式<br />\n而唔係數字遊戲<br />\n不過暴雪都唔會出Diablo4架喇<br />\n<br />\n幾年冇玩最近番去玩秘法師<br />\n悶到爆棄game有感而發"},{"pid":"018f4eacd42e1cb91404360f7f189da45614a16a","tid":893280,"uid":39360,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:29:36.000Z","msg":"嗯<br />\n主機上首次有中文結果switch 獨佔<br />\n這種心情我能理解"},{"pid":"691a17411003e61c84594b2ead5dc3acb1c3d87d","tid":893280,"uid":94828,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"018f4eacd42e1cb91404360f7f189da45614a16a","tid":893280,"uid":39360,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:29:36.000Z","msg":"嗯<br />\n主機上首次有中文結果switch 獨佔<br />\n這種心情我能理解"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"唔好咁敏感啦<br />\n人地連主機都冇提過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d808cd50545136e530e49e28ee87fd8972d11ff","tid":893280,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:32:25.000Z","msg":"當年第2代好玩到唔肯訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，家陣玩一陣第3代就悶到想訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"1c312b1dce2b6bf87004bd1d6ff503d7be8293d3","tid":893280,"uid":220754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"玩到第3代真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我寧願返去POE"},{"pid":"639ca3115d88cb9d957578e1e9814e7b512